config.script: self.getChild("root").getChild("Monthly Peak Container").getChild("Charts Container").getChild("Monthly Peak Chart Container").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("FlexContainer_1").getChild("BillingMonth").props.value = system.date.getMonth(system.date.now())

transforms.code:
value = 'Opto22'
	value = self.custom.org
	path = "[ESN]" + value + "/EdgeNodes"
	results = system.tag.browse(path)

	final = []
	for node in results:
		if node["hasChildren"]:
			node["energyLoads"] = [system.tag.browse(str(node["fullPath"]) + "/Loads")]
		
		final.append(node)
	return final
